  m_text: "<align=center><size=55><b>Privacy Policy</b></size></align>\r\n\r\nThis
    application (\"the App\") is provided by the developer (\"we,\" \"us,\" or \"our\").
    We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your information responsibly.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>1.
    Information We Collect</b></size>\r\nWe do <b>not</b> collect personal information
    that can directly identify you.\r\nThe App may collect limited technical data
    automatically, such as:\r\n\u2022 Device type\r\n\u2022 Operating system version\r\n\u2022
    General usage interactions\r\n  This information is used solely to improve app
    performance and user experience.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>2. How We Use Information</b></size>\r\nAny
    collected data is used only for:\r\n\u2022 App functionality\r\n\u2022 Performance
    optimization\r\n\u2022 Basic analytics to understand general usage trends\r\nWe
    do not use data for tracking, personalized advertising, or sharing with third
    parties for marketing purposes.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>3. Third-Party Services</b></size>\r\nSome
    features may rely on third-party SDKs (e.g., analytics or ad networks).  \r\nThese
    partners may process non-personal, device-level information to support app operations
    in accordance with their own privacy policies.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>4. Data Sharing</b></size>\r\nWe
    do not sell, trade, or share personal data with any third party.  \r\nAggregated
    and non-identifiable technical data may be used for analytics or app diagnostics.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>5.
    Children's Privacy</b></size>\r\nThis App is intended for general audiences and
    is not directed to children.  \r\nWe do not knowingly collect personal information
    from users under the applicable age of digital consent.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>6.
    Data Security</b></size>\r\nWe implement reasonable technical and organizational
    measures to protect data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>7.
    Your Rights</b></size>\r\nDepending on your region, you may have rights to request
    deletion, access, or restriction of data processing.  \r\nYou may contact us
    for any such request.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>8. Changes to This Policy</b></size>\r\nWe
    may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the App means
    you accept the updated terms.\r\n\r\n<size=40><b>9. Contact Us</b></size>\r\nIf
    you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:  \r\n
    <u>rodrigues@pascualandina.com</u> "
